This model software representation was created based on the model developed by Kelsey et al This class facilitates the calculation of the AMH results based on the statistical model by Kelsey et al 2011 Article can be accessed at: http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?artid=3137624&tool=pmcentrez&rendertype=abstract
